title: Alec Baldwin fired prop gun that killed photography chief, injured director on film set | ABC7
author: ABC7
description: Actor Alec Baldwin has been identified as the person who fired a prop firearm that killed a crew member and left director Joel Souza hospitalized in an incident on the set of a Western being filmed in New Mexico.
